{"tid":1500724,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"希望各位能以不同方式發聲","createTime":"2019-08-24T06:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T06:43:07.000Z","uid":190025,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0e97d738869f27e106e66b84bb659439ee63f500","tid":1500724,"uid":190025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:17:14.000Z","msg":"讓世界各地更多人能關注香港<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，決一不可！</span></span></strong></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n利申：代友出post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本人最近砌了這個小作，發佈到各個樂高的群組及平台，希望藉此在國際樂高界為活動及香港的情況，稍為對外發聲。如果可以的話，請各位轉發給身邊好友。冀能鼓勵更多各方賢能，以自己的方法發聲。香港加油！<br />\n<br />\n一位香港市民及樂高愛好者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZDujvS3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZDujvS3.jpg&h=68eeba49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5GErVjK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5GErVjK.jpg&h=bd0b01ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EAOPS6k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAOPS6k.jpg&h=487fa831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t9M6aS2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft9M6aS2.jpg&h=fa901efd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7B0KGZN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7B0KGZN.jpg&h=0039d10d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gE2w6rr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgE2w6rr.jpg&h=66cad3a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49731c5affb6e8660ba4b40ccde40ec2bfd63ec2","tid":1500724,"uid":190025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:17:46.000Z","msg":"自推十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737e823b3b25a8744c73ae67a5c89cc6b7274873","tid":150